a fast division technique for constant divisors.wa fast algorithm for division by constant divisorsis presented.  the method has proved very useful implemented as microcode ona binary machine,and can be adapted directly into hardware.  the mathematical foundations of the algorithm are presentedas well as some performance measures.cacm february, artzy, e.hinds, j. a.saal, h. j..kconstant divisors, division algorithms,bit addressable memory, microprogram.c. . .ca jb january ,   : am